# dmg-assets/

This directory holds DMG layout assets — primarily `background.png` (660x400)
used by `scripts/package-dmg.sh` and the CI release workflow.

v0.0.1 ships with a placeholder dark-grey PNG. v0.1+ replaces it with a designed
background. Per CONTEXT.md D-16, when `background.png` is absent, the packaging
script falls back to the no-background two-icon layout — that codepath is verified
by removing this file locally and re-running `scripts/package-dmg.sh`.
